Expected result:

 postgres   | Superuser, Create role, Create DB, Replication, Bypass RLS | {}
 vc         | Create DB                                                  | {}

If the accounts other than "postgres" and "vc" have any "Create" privileges, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
