					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>At the command prompt, execute the following command:

# grep -v "^#" /storage/db/vpostgres/pg_hba.conf|grep -z --color=always "trust"

If any lines are returned, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
