					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>At the command prompt, execute the following command:

# /opt/vmware/vpostgres/current/bin/psql -U postgres -c "REVOKE ALL PRIVILEGES ON &lt;name&gt; FROM &lt;user&gt;;"

Replace &lt;name&gt; and &lt;user&gt; with the Access Privilege name and account, respectively, discovered during the check.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
